				<h1>BAYADA Pediatrics</h1>
				<h2>Exceptional care for your childâ€¦peace of mind for you.</h2>

				<p>At BAYADA Pediatrics, our professionals specialize in caring for children of all ages, from newborns to adolescents, at home and at school. Our compassionate, carefully screened, and experienced BAYADA Pediatric Nurses manage diverse diagnoses and high-tech equipment, while our highly trained and caring BAYADA Pediatric Home Health Aides provide assistive personal care and support services.</p>

				<p>We take a family-centered approach and partner with you in your child's care. In working together, our clients and families experience firsthand our team's shared commitment to compassion, excellence, and reliability &mdash; the core values of <span class="italics"><a class="go" rel="leanModal" href="#BayadaWay">The BAYADA Way</a></span>.</p>

				<h2>Who is on my child&#8217;s care team?</h2>
				<p>BAYADA Pediatric Nurses and <a class="go" rel="leanModal" href="#HHA">Home Health Aides</a> are experts in caring for children from newborns to adolescents, including those requiring complex, high-tech care.</p>
				<p>Depending on their needs, your child&#8217;s care team may include one or more:</p>
                				<ul>
						<li><span class="bold">BAYADA Nurses</span> &mdash; provide nursing services ranging from short-term recovery care to ongoing nursing and high-tech care</li>
						<li><span class="bold">BAYADA Home Health Aides</span> &mdash; assist with non-medical activities of daily living like bathing, dressing, exercises, and meal preparation</li>
                				</ul><br>
				<p>Your child&#8217;s care team also includes a registered nurse (RN) clinical manager (oversees clinical care and makes in-home visits), a client services manager (ensures satisfaction and coordinates services), and an on-call manager (addresses questions or concerns after-hours).</p>

				<p>Visit our other pediatric pages to learn more about our pediatric <a href="/services-pediatrics-nursing.asp">nursing</a> and <a href="/services-pediatrics-assistive-care.asp">assistive care</a> services, our <a href="/our-care-professionals.asp">health care professionals</a>, and how we can help your child at <a href="/services-pediatrics-school.asp">school</a>.</p>

				<p>You can also visit the <a href="/faq.asp">FAQs page</a> for answers to our most frequently asked questions.</p><br><br>

